   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>25</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Fix <fr:link href="/jms-00KR/" title="Bijection" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KR/" display-uri="jms-00KR" type="local">bijections</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  X]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  B \to  Y]]></fr:tex>. We will define a bijection <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H\colon  \mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}\to  \mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left (X,Y\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>

 <html:p>Given <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex>, we define <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H{\mathopen {}\left (R\right )\mathclose {}}\colon  X\mathbin {\nrightarrow } Y]]></fr:tex> to be the <fr:link href="/jms-00IN/" title="Relational composite" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00IN/" display-uri="jms-00IN" type="local">relational composite</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  R\circ  f^{-1}]]></fr:tex>. The inverse mapping <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H^{-1}\colon \mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left (X,Y\right )\mathclose {}}\to \mathrm {Rel}{\mathopen {}\left (A,B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is defined to take <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S\colon  X\mathbin {\nrightarrow } Y]]></fr:tex> to the <fr:link href="/jms-00IN/" title="Relational composite" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00IN/" display-uri="jms-00IN" type="local">relational composite</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g^{-1} \circ  S\circ  f]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>

 <html:p>Next, we check that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H^{-1}]]></fr:tex> is simulatneously a <fr:link href="/jms-00KS/" title="Section-retraction pair" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KS/" display-uri="jms-00KS" type="local">retraction</fr:link> and a <fr:link href="/jms-00KS/" title="Section-retraction pair" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00KS/" display-uri="jms-00KS" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>

 <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
   H^{-1}{\mathopen {}\left (H{\mathopen {}\left (R\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}} &= g^{-1}\circ  H{\mathopen {}\left (R\right )\mathclose {}}\circ  f\\
   &= g^{-1}\circ  {\mathopen {}\left (g\circ  R\circ  f^{-1}\right )\mathclose {}}\circ  f\\
   &= {\mathopen {}\left (g^{-1}\circ  g\right )\mathclose {}}\circ  R\circ  {\mathopen {}\left (f^{-1}\circ  f\right )\mathclose {}}\\
   &= \mathsf {id}_{B}\circ  R\circ  \mathsf {id}_{A}\\
